      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "On the basis of our experience along with an encouraging previous report of hypofractionated intensity modulated RT (IMRT) plus weekly gemcitabine that showed a response rate of 88% in frail patients with MIBC and based on the above and similar findings, we initiated a phase I clinical trial of everolimus plus TMT to establish the toxicity of the combination and to potentially validate our hypothesis that this approach would improve local control of disease."
